articles.author: George Megalogenis
articles.title: On Scott Morrison’s watch, Australia has lost standing on the world stage - Sydney Morning Herald
articles.description: What is unique about the prime minister’s position is the accumulation of bad blood.
articles.content:
What is unique about Morrisons position is the accumulation of bad blood. No prime minister since Billy Hughes has had this many disputes running at the same time.
